    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crack your <strong>egg[s]</strong> into a wide bowl and add 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml] </span><strong>milk </strong>and the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>curry powder</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>egg mixture</strong></p><p>Dip the <strong>halved ciabatta</strong>,<strong> </strong>cut side down, into the<strong> egg mixture </strong>until it's been absorbed by the bread – this is your <strong>curried ciabatta</strong></p>",
